# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11833
msgid "Although most hardware devices are supported by the Debian system, there are some network devices which require <ulink url=\"&dsfg;\">DSFG</ulink> non-free external hardware drivers to support them.  Please see <xref linkend=\"_non_free_hardware_drivers\"/>."
msgstr "La plupart des périphériques matériels sont pris en charge par le système Debian, il y a quelques périphériques de réseau qui exigent, pour les gérer, des pilotes matériels non libres selon <ulink url=\"&dsfg;\">DSFG</ulink>. Veuillez consulter <xref linkend=\"_non_free_hardware_drivers\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11837
msgid "The modern network configuration for desktop"
msgstr "Configuration moderne de réseau pour l’ordinateur de bureau"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11838
msgid "Debian <literal>squeeze</literal> systems can manage the network connection via management <ulink url=\"&daemon;\">daemon</ulink> software such as <ulink url=\"&networkmanagernm;\">NetworkManager (NM)</ulink> (network-manager and associated packages) or <ulink url=\"&wicd;\">Wicd</ulink> (wicd and associated packages)."
msgstr "Les systèmes Debian <literal>squeeze</literal> peuvent gérer la connexion au réseau à l’aide de <ulink url=\"&daemon;\">démons</ulink> tels que <ulink url=\"&networkmanagernm;\">NetworkManager (NM)</ulink> (paquet network-manager et les paquets associés) ou <ulink url=\"&wicd;\">Wicd</ulink> (paquet wicd et les paquets associés)."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11842
msgid "They come with their own <ulink url=\"&gui;\">GUI</ulink> and command-line programs as their user interfaces."
msgstr "Il sont fournis avec leur propre interface utilisateur graphique (<ulink url=\"&gui;\">GUI</ulink>) et en ligne de commandes."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11847
msgid "They come with their own <ulink url=\"&daemon;\">daemon</ulink> as their backend system."
msgstr "Ils ont leur propre <ulink url=\"&daemon;\">démon</ulink> en tant que sytème dorsal."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11852
msgid "They allow easy connection of your system to the Internet."
msgstr "Ils permettent une connexion facile de votre système à Internet."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11857
msgid "They allow easy management of wired and wireless network configuration."
msgstr "Ils permettent une gestion facile de la configuration du réseau filaire ou sans fil."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11862
msgid "They allow us to configure network independent of the legacy <literal>ifupdown</literal> package."
msgstr "Ils nous permettent de configurer le réseau indépendamment de l’ancien paquet «&nbsp;<literal>ifupdown</literal>&nbsp;»"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><warning><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><note><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11867
msgid "Do not use these automatic network configuration tools for servers.  These are aimed primarily for mobile desktop users on laptops."
msgstr "Ne pas utiliser ces outils de configuration automatique du réseau sur un serveur. Ils ont été prévus principalement pour les utilisateurs de système de bureau tournant sur des ordinateurs portables."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11869
msgid "These modern network configuration tools need to be configured properly to avoid conflicting with the legacy <literal>ifupdown</literal> package and its configuration file \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\"."
msgstr "Ce outils moderne de configuration du réseau doivent être configurés correctement afin d’éviter des conflits avec l’ancien paquet <literal>ifupdown</literal> et son fichier de configuration «&nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;»."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><caution><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><note><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11871
msgid "Some features of these automatic network configuration tools may suffer regressions.  These are not as robust as the legacy <literal>ifupdown</literal> package.  Check <ulink url=\"&btsofnetworkmanager;\">BTS of network-manager</ulink> and <ulink url=\"&btsofwicd;\">BTS of wicd</ulink> for current issues and limitations."
msgstr "Certaines fonctionnalités de ces outils de configuration automatique du réseau peuvent souffrir de régressions. Ils ne sont pas aussi robustes que l’ancien paquet <literal>ifupdown</literal>. Consultez le <ulink url=\"&btsofnetworkmanager;\">BTS de network-manager</ulink> et le <ulink url=\"&btsofwicd;\">BTS de wicd</ulink> pour en savoir plus sur les problèmes et les limitations actuels."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11874
msgid "GUI network configuration tools"
msgstr "Outils graphiques de configuration du réseau"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11875
msgid "Official documentations for NM and Wicd on Debian are provided in \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/network-manager/README.Debian</literal>\" and \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/wicd/README.Debian</literal>\", respectively."
msgstr "Les documentations officielles de NM et Wicd sous Debian sont fournies respectivement par «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/doc/network-manager/README.Debian</literal>&nbsp;» et «&nbsp;<literal>/usr/share/doc/wicd/README.Debian</literal>&nbsp;»."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11876
msgid "Essentially, the network configuration for desktop is done as follows."
msgstr "Essentiellement, la onfiguration réseau pour l’ordinateur de bureau est faite de la manière suivante&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11880
msgid "Make desktop user, e.g. <literal>foo</literal>, belong to group \"<literal>netdev</literal>\" by the following (Alternatively, do it automatically via <ulink url=\"&dbus;\">D-bus</ulink> under modern desktop environments such as GNOME and KDE)."
msgstr "Rendez l’utilisateur du bureau, par exemple <literal>toto</literal>, membre du groupe «&nbsp;<literal>netdev</literal>&nbsp;» à l’aide de la commande suivante (vous pouvez aussi le faire automatiquement à l’aide de <ulink url=\"&dbus;\">D-bus</ulink> sous les environnements de bureau modernes comme GNOME et KDE)&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><screen>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11882
#, no-wrap
msgid "$ sudo adduser foo netdev"
msgstr "$ sudo adduser toto netdev"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:11886
msgid "Keep configuration of \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" as simple as the the following."
msgstr "Gardez la configuration de «&nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;» aussi simple que possible comme ce qui suit&nbsp;:"

