"iface ppp0 inet ppp\n"
" provider &lt;nom_fai&gt;"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12795
msgid "The alternative PPP connection"
msgstr "La connexion alternative PPP"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12796
msgid "You need to configure the alternative PPP connection with <literal>wvdial</literal> first as described before (see <xref linkend=\"_the_alternative_ppp_connection_with_wvdialconf\"/>).  Then, add the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file entry for the primary PPP device <literal>ppp0</literal> as the following."
msgstr "Vous devrez d'abord configurer la connexion PPP alternative avec <literal>wvdial</literal> comme décrit précédemment (voir <xref linkend=\"_the_alternative_ppp_connection_with_wvdialconf\"/>). Ajoutez ensuite dans le fichier «&nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;» une entrée pour le périphérique primaire PPP <literal>ppp0</literal> comme suit&nbsp;:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12797
#, no-wrap
msgid "iface ppp0 inet wvdial"
msgstr "iface ppp0 inet wvdial"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12800
msgid "The PPPoE connection"
msgstr "La connexion PPPoE"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12801
msgid "For PC connected directly to the WAN served by the PPPoE, you need to configure system with the PPPoE connection as described before (see <xref linkend=\"_the_pppoe_connection_with_pppoeconf\"/>).  Then, add the \"<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>\" file entry for the primary PPPoE device <literal>eth0</literal> as the following."
msgstr "Pour le PC directement connecté au WAN et utilisant PPPoE, vous devez configurer votre système pour une connexion PPPoE comme cela a été décrit précédemment (voir <xref linkend=\"_the_pppoe_connection_with_pppoeconf\"/>). Ajoutez ensuite dans le fichier «&nbsp;<literal>/etc/network/interfaces</literal>&nbsp;» une entrée pour le premier périphérique PPPoE <literal>eth0</literal> comme suit&nbsp;:"

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12802
