#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13730
msgid "You see <literal>ping</literal>(8) succeed with 1454."
msgstr "Vous voyez que <literal>ping</literal>(8) a réussi avec 1454."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13731
msgid "This process is <ulink url=\"&pathmtupmtudiscovery;\">Path MTU (PMTU) discovery</ulink> (<ulink url=\"&rfcbbjb;\">RFC1191</ulink>) and the <literal>tracepath</literal>(8) command can automate this."
msgstr "Ce processus est la <ulink url=\"&pathmtupmtudiscovery;\">découverte du chemin MTU (PMTU)</ulink> (<ulink url=\"&rfcbbjb;\">RFC1191</ulink>) et la commande <literal>tracepath</literal>(8) peut l’automatiser."

# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
