# type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:17677
msgid "In order to save space for <ulink url=\"&truetype;\">TrueType</ulink> font files, <ulink url=\"&truetype;\">TrueType</ulink> font collection file with file extension \"<literal>.ttc</literal>\" may be used."
